'''Bhuru''' (bull in English) i[[mombe]] [[hono]] isina kuchekwa. Iyi ndiwo mukono unokwanisa kubereka. Bhuru rinoonekwa ne[[nyundwa]] uye [[machende]] mahombe akarembera. Bhuru rinotaurwawo pamukono wedzimwe mhuka dzinosanganisira [[nyati]], [[nzou]]; [[mhofu]]; [[nhoro]]; [[ngwarati]] nedzimwewo.

Mamwe mazita anoshandiswa ndeekuti [[ngunzi]] kana kuti [[handira]].

